        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on forthcoming edition [7th (1847)] of CL’s <hi rend="italic">Principles</hi>. Mentions other books relevant to CL’s needs by Hooker, H. G. Bronn, Edward Forbes, and J. G. Kölreuter. Discusses his own books on volcanoes and the geology of S. America.</p> 
            <p>Mentions expected visit to Down by the Lyells.</p>
        </abstract>
